The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Bopanna to face Fish
                                                                                                                                                                                                     Bopanna to face Fish
                      
	New Delhi: Indian Davis Cupper Rohan Bopanna set up a second round clash with top seed Mardy Fish after defeating Kim Kevin in straight sets at the $385,000 Campbells Hall of Fame tennis championships in Newport.         
	Bopanna pipped his American opponent 6-3, 6-4 in one hour and 11 minutes on Monday. Both the players struggled in converting the breakpoints and squandered numerous chances.         
	Bopanna could convert just three of 10 while Kevin converted just one of the nine breakpoints that came his way.But Bopanna lived upto his reputation of being a booming server firing 15 aces as against one of Kevin.         
	Bopanna, who is ranked 374, has a tough test in the second round as he is up against a player, who is ranked as high as 41 in the ATP ranking charts. Fish got a bye in the first round.         
	(PTI)                                                                                                                          
